thread.title: BRIEF-Vente-Unique.Com IPO priced at 10.70 euros per share

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Vente-Unique.Com IPO priced at 10.70 euros per share
text:
March 28 (Reuters) - VENTE-UNIQUE.COM SA:
* RAISES EUR 7 MILLION IN IPO * IPO: GLOBAL DEMAND REPRESESENTS 1.8 TIMES NUMBER OF SHARES OFFERED
* TRADING IN SHARES TO BEGIN ON APRIL 4 * TOTAL AMOUNT OF PLACEMENT EUR 32.8 MILLION AFTER EXERCISE OF 100 PERCENT OF EXTENSION CLAUSE
* AT END OF OPERATION, CAPITAL CONSISTS OF 9.4 MILLION SHARES, REPRESENTING MARKET CAPITALIZATION OF EUR 101 MILLION
* TOTAL AMOUNT OF PLACEMENT COULD RISE TO EUR 37.7 MILLION IF OVER ALLOTMENT OPTION EXERCISED IN FULL Source text: bit.ly/2pOSwmi Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom:)
